headline: CENTENE APPOINTS KENNETH Y. TANJI TO BOARD OF DIRECTORS
summary: Centene Corporation (NYSE: CNC) ("the Company") announced today the appointment of Kenneth Y. Tanji to the Centene Board of Directors, effective February 20, 2025. Mr. Tanji will serve on the Company's Audit and Compliance Committee. The appointment of Mr. Tanji expands Centene's Board of Directors to 12 members.

headline: MD Gains 11% Since Q4 Earnings Release, Unveils '25 View
summary: Pediatrix Medical's fourth-quarter results reflect a declining overall expense level. It estimates 2025 net income to lie within $98.3-$112.9 million.
